<article class="blog--container blog-preview">
<h2 class="blog--title">
<a href="/blog/2012/05/07/spring-mvc-3-2-preview-introducing-servlet-3-async-support">Spring MVC 3.2 Preview: Introducing Servlet 3, Async Support</a>
</h2>
<header class="meta-data--container">
